# S01-T10: App Shell with HUD Layout (7-Slot System)

## Objective
Port the 7-slot HUD layout from drone-interface/6 to React with Tailwind CSS and Framer Motion. All motion must comply with UI_REGULATION.ti — state communication, NOT decoration.

## Design Regulation Compliance
- Motion: 200-260ms panel transitions. No bounce/spring/elastic/overshoot.
- Layout: TOP=status, CENTER=video+HUD, BOTTOM=graphs
- Video is primary, UI is secondary
- HUD must NOT block center targeting area
- Borders: `1px solid rgba(26,205,179,0.3)`, corners 4-8px

## Acceptance Criteria
- `src/app/App.tsx` — Root component with providers + router
- `src/app/providers.tsx` — QueryClientProvider + ErrorBoundary wrapper
- `src/features/hud/components/HudLayout.tsx` — 7-slot absolute layout:
  - `topLeft`: Connection status (20px from edges)
  - `topCenter`: Slot control panel (centered)
  - `topRight`: Battery indicator (20px from right)
  - `centerLeft`: Radar (vertically centered, left edge)
  - `centerRight`: Attitude gauges (vertically centered, right edge)
  - `bottom`: Telemetry graphs (full width, 20px from bottom)
  - `debug`: Full-overlay diagnostics panel (z-20)
- Tailwind: `bg-transparent pointer-events-none` on overlay, `pointer-events-auto` on slots
- **Framer Motion** entry animations (regulation-compliant):
  - Duration: `200ms` (`duration: 0.2`)
  - Easing: `ease-out` (no spring physics)
  - `topLeft`: `initial={{ x: -40, opacity: 0 }}` → `animate={{ x: 0, opacity: 1 }}`
  - `topCenter`: `initial={{ y: -40, opacity: 0 }}`
  - `topRight`: `initial={{ x: 40, opacity: 0 }}`
  - `bottom`: `initial={{ y: 40, opacity: 0 }}`
  - `debug`: `initial={{ opacity: 0 }}` → fade in (no scale)
- `AnimatePresence` for slot show/hide (immediate exit, 200ms enter)
- Responsive: `md:` breakpoint for tablet adjustments
- `src/features/hud/components/TacticalHud.tsx` — Main view composing placeholder widgets

## Loading States (regulation-compliant)
When telemetry not connected:
```
ACQUIRING VIDEO SIGNAL...
SYNCING TELEMETRY...
```
NO spinners. Blinking cyan text with `animate={{ opacity: [1, 0.3, 1] }}`.

## Steps
1. Create providers.tsx (QueryClient + Router)
2. Create HudLayout with absolute Tailwind positioning
3. Add Framer Motion 200ms slide-in (ease-out, no spring)
4. Add AnimatePresence for slot toggling
5. Create TacticalHud with placeholder widgets
6. Add loading states (signal acquisition style)
7. Wire into App.tsx with router
